  "detail": {
    "tagExpireTime": "1755682948762",
    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1272537988114550784",
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2436\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》</span></a>，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年8月13日- 2025年8月19日，规则预计于2025年8月20日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心调整点：价格违规程度和处理措施拆分为一般、严重、特别严重三级。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">修订内容如下：</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; background: white; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 25.54%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"25%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 37.22%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"37%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 37.24%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"37%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 25.54%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"25%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十三条 各类价格违规行为</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-align: start; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">【处理措施】</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 37.22%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"37%\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">若商家发生违反本规则或经消费者投诉发现商家存在价格违规行为的，京东有权依据法律法规、平台规则及协议等进行处理，并有权视违规程度采取包括但不限于预警、下架违规商品、限制营销活动、限制广告活动、降低店铺星级、要求商家支付50元以上1000000元以下违约金、加收保证金、搜推屏蔽/降权、商品详情页屏蔽、限制区域销售、限制商品上架/发布、钱包冻结、类目/品牌停用、店铺关停清退等处理措施。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 37.24%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"37%\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度分级</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">一般违规：存在价格违规行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">严重违规：通过价格违规手段牟取不当利益，或多次违反平台规则。出现包括但不限于以下任一情形：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 累计触发3次及以上一般违规；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 价格违规获取不当得利的；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 发生客诉或舆情的；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">极其严重违规：恶意对抗平台规则、造成重大客诉、舆情或平台重大利益损失。出现包括但不限于以下任一情形：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 累计触发10次及以上一般违规；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 通过各种手段，逃避平台处置、对抗平台规则的；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 价格违规造成严重后果、被追究或可能追究行政或刑事责任等情形的；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 产生重大客诉或舆情；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">客诉与舆情判定标准</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 平台内客诉：用户通过订单评价、在线客服、投诉工单等官方渠道反馈价格问题；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 社会化媒体舆情：用户于微信、微博、抖音、小红书等公共平台发布价格违规证据；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">被主流媒体转载报道或登上社交平台热搜榜单；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 政府监管介入：用户向市监局、消协、法院等部门举报/诉讼；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">处置规则</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 违规程度一般的：平台会采取包括但不限于预警、搜推降权/屏蔽、下架违规商品、限制营销活动、限制广告活动、降低店铺星级、限制商品上架/发布、钱包/账户冻结、类目/品牌停用等；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 违规程度严重的：平台会采取包括但不限于预警、搜推降权/屏蔽、下架违规商品、限制营销活动、限制广告活动、降低店铺星级、限制商品上架/发布、钱包资金冻结、处以商家50元以上20000元以下违约金等处置；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 15.75pt; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">） 违规程度极其严重的：平台会采取包括但不限于搜推降权/屏蔽、禁止营销/广告活动、降低店铺星级、全店商品下架、禁止商品上架/发布、类目/品牌停用、店铺关停清退等处置，同时视恶意程度冻结账户、处以商家20000元以上1000000元以下违约金等处置。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; background: white; word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
